1.title: Stealing Chickens and Making Money
1.plot: Dwayne and his brother Tom explore their origins while sharing troubles.

2.title: Not Just Two
2.plot: Tom relentlessly hounds his brother Dwayne for 'seed money', however Dwayne has a new idea in that direction.

3.title: White Trash Slut
3.plot: Tom gets an unexpected response (and offer) from Susanne when he solicits her for money.

4.title: Five Gears Short of a Sex Pact
4.plot: Dwayne visits Tom for a change and Susanne has to renegotiate some previous "business" arrangements with Tom.

5.title: Jenny from the Stock
5.plot: We get to finally meet Jenny and find out what she is all about, as well as see what is so 'mysterious' about Dwayne.

6.title: All's Well When Ends Swell
6.plot: Tom is confused between airplanes and buses, while Dwayne reassures himself with Jenny as Susanne confronts Tom. Finally, passions are heightened when Tom and Jenny finally meet and begin making plans.
